title: Dex Enhanced Edition v5 4-PLAZA
description:
Dex Enhanced Edition v5.4.0.0 (c) Badland Games, Techland

Release Date: 06/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action, RPG

Discover the truth behind an enigmatic AI striving to reach the
Singularity, a theoretical event horizon in which artificial
intelligence will surpass human intelligence and all bets about the
future will be off. How will you play your part in the story?

Explore the futuristic city of Harbor Prime and meet its many
inhabitants, answer the challenges the city has to offer, roam the
neon-lit streets, and augment your character with skills and implants

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/269650/

1. Mount ISO
2. Install the game
3. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
4. Play!

NOTES:
We were going to do an update, but it turned out to be the same
size of the entire game. So instead here is a fully updated release
